33:06.767 --> 33:09.639
♪ WHOO WHOO

33:09.770 --> 33:11.772
-IT'S HIM! HOBIE, LOOK!

33:11.902 --> 33:13.687
THAT'S THE GUY!

33:13.817 --> 33:16.516
-DAD! DAD, THAT'S THE GUY
