-TONY: GET OFF OF
ME, YOU LITTLE CREEPS!

36:15.608 --> 36:19.133
-YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO REMAIN SILENT.

36:19.264 --> 36:20.134
HO HO.

36:24.486 --> 36:25.618
-TAKE THAT!

36:27.924 --> 36:32.886
-[WHIMSICAL MUSIC]

36:43.375 --> 36:44.811
-FATHER, WE GOT
ONE JUST FOR YOU.

36:45.464 --> 36:47.074
-THIS IS FOR ME?
-BENNY: HEY, MERRY
CHRISTMAS TO ALL OF YOU.

36:47.205 --> 36:47.988
-YEAH.

36:48.118 --> 36:48.989
-THANKS.

36:54.560 --> 36:55.343
I DON'T BELIEVE IT.

36:55.474 --> 36:56.736
-[LAUGHING]

36:56.866 --> 36:58.303
WHERE COULD THIS HAVE COME FROM?

36:59.042 --> 37:02.002
-EVERYTHING'S DONATED.
WE HAVE NO WAY OF
KNOWING WHO TO THANK.

37:02.132 --> 37:04.352
-THAT SHOULD BE ENOUGH TO
HELP THE CHURCH AND THE KIDS.

37:09.749 --> 37:10.967
-HEY, MOM!

37:11.098 --> 37:12.534
THAT'S OUR MONEY!

37:12.665 --> 37:13.709
IT BELONGS TO US!

37:14.362 --> 37:16.799
-NO, JOEY, I THINK IT'S
EXACTLY WHERE IT BELONGS.

37:17.322 --> 37:19.280
EXACTLY WHERE
IT NEEDS TO STAY.

37:19.411 --> 37:21.717
LISTEN HONEY, I THINK IT'S TIME

37:21.848 --> 37:23.023
WE TURN OVER A NEW LEAF.

37:23.719 --> 37:24.590
STARTING TODAY.

37:25.591 --> 37:26.983
MERRY CHRISTMAS, BABY.

37:28.681 --> 37:30.335
-YEAH, BUT, MOM, I
HAD THIS GREAT IDEA!

37:31.161 --> 37:32.380
WHY CAN'T WE TURN OVER
A NEW LEAF TOMORROW?

37:32.511 --> 37:33.338
-TODAY.

37:33.468 --> 37:34.904
AND THAT'S FINAL.

37:35.035 --> 37:37.037
COME ON, LET'S GO SLEDDING.

37:37.167 --> 37:38.168
[LAUGHING]

37:39.169 --> 37:40.519
[SQUEALING]

37:47.090 --> 37:48.744
-WELL, TO TELL YOU THE TRUTH,

37:48.875 --> 37:50.398
THIS HAS BEEN THE
BEST CHRISTMAS EVER.

37:50.529 --> 37:52.835
-WELL, EVEN THOUGH I
REALLY MISS STEPHANIE,

37:52.966 --> 37:54.750
I HAVE TO ADMIT I HAD
A PRETTY GREAT DAY.

37:56.012 --> 37:57.710
-ME, TOO.

37:57.840 --> 37:59.102
EVEN THOUGH BENNY AND HIS
GANG AREN'T REALLY ELVES.

38:00.669 --> 38:02.584
THEY TOLD ME THEY
WERE A BOWLING TEAM.

38:02.715 --> 38:04.107
-[LAUGHING]
-WAIT A MINUTE,

38:04.238 --> 38:05.718
THEY TOLD ME THEY WERE
ROCKET SCIENTISTS.

38:05.848 --> 38:07.589
-WAIT, THEY TOLD ME
THEY WERE UNDERTAKERS.

38:07.720 --> 38:09.548
-I THINK THEY'RE ELVES.

38:09.678 --> 38:10.897
-I'M CONVINCED.

38:11.027 --> 38:13.203
-SO AM I.

38:13.334 --> 38:15.075
IF IT WEREN'T FOR THEM,
WE WOULDN'T HAVE GOTTEN
THE SNOW MACHINE IN TIME.

38:15.205 --> 38:16.729
-AND WE WOULD'VE NEVER PULLED
OFF THIS INCREDIBLE SURPRISE.

38:16.859 --> 38:18.078
-RIGHT.

38:18.208 --> 38:19.209
-HOW DID THEY PULL
OFF THIS THING?

38:19.340 --> 38:20.994
-I WAS AFRAID TO ASK.

38:21.124 --> 38:22.865
-WELL, I'M JUST GONNA HAVE
TO THANK THEM PERSONALLY.

38:22.996 --> 38:24.780
-WELL...

38:24.911 --> 38:26.260
BENNY GAVE ME HIS ADDRESS IF
I EVER WANT TO WRITE TO HIM

38:26.391 --> 38:28.218
OR IF I EVER NEEDED ANYTHING.

38:29.132 --> 38:30.786
-WAIT A SECOND, WHAT IS THIS?

38:30.917 --> 38:32.962
THIS IS A CHRISTMAS
WISH LIST FORM.

38:33.093 --> 38:35.225
OH MY GOD, LOOK AT
THIS, LOOK AT THIS.

38:36.226 --> 38:37.402
-BENNY THE ELF?

38:37.532 --> 38:39.360
CARE OF KRIS KRINGLE?

38:39.491 --> 38:41.057
-ALL: NORTH POLE!

38:41.188 --> 38:42.320
-YEAH, RIGHT.
-[LAUGHING]

38:44.234 --> 38:45.192
-I TOLD YOU THEY WERE ELVES.

38:45.323 --> 38:46.106
-THEY'RE ELVES.

38:46.236 --> 38:47.281
-YES.

38:47.412 --> 38:48.804
-THIS IS BEAUTIFUL, MITCH.

38:48.935 --> 38:51.154
ALL THAT'S MISSING
IS A CHRISTMAS CAROL.

38:51.285 --> 38:54.070
